Title: The Sky's the Limit
Plot: Pete and Myka head to Vegas to investigate murders that are tied to the world of high magic. Meanwhile, Claudia and Jinks search for an artifact used to rig horse races, while Artie meets the new B&B owner, Abigail Cho.
GuestStars: Polly Walker, Joel Grey, Kelly Hu, Nora Zehetner, Steve Valentine, CCH Pounder, Goldy Notay, Tara Joshi
